				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Actually... on the topic of magi ideas...  we should be able to bind wherever the hell we want.
<br />

<br />
To allow this to happen... we would on death, appear outside the gates of our city of creation, not bind point. We can gate there if we friggin want.
<br />

<br />
This would make our tailsman or return VERY handy indeed for ping ponging back and forth while on those annoying trips where you need something in the bank. Or to sell all your booty and come back for more in a flash. 
<br />

<br />
Not to mention you would only need one magi to do a CoH alone on raids! No more need for a wiz / druid for a class defining spell to be max handy on raids!
<br />

<br />
We might not be the masters of travel but I would like the increased functionality of planning my travel with a little more flexability.
<br />

