or tanks </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
Very true.  Magicians are masters of summoning.  Our pets should make fairly good makeshift tanks however.
<br />

<br />
I totally agree that magician pet heals are very likely our least efficient spells for damage/mana vs. XP mobs.  This seems to have always been the case.  As a result, I hardly ever use them in an XP situation.
<br />

<br />
On the other side of things, beastlords use their pet heals frequently when soloing, offtanking, and in pet groups.  Magicians have other options.
<br />

<br />
I am not a chaining advocate because I like playing god with my pets' lives, but rather it is the most mana efficient approach I have access to.  If SOE changes things so that our pet heals are a better idea, then I will change my playstyle accordingly.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
