				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">And yet ...
<br />

<br />
It could be that magicians dont have such an ability so that they are dependent on another class.  Remember that, all solo capabilities aside, players are encouraged to group with each other, not the other way around.  A magician that needs another class to complete a task may look 'incomplete' to your eyes, but may seem 'complementary to another class' in the developers' eyes.
<br />

<br />
Not every class has to be self-sufficient in every regard to achieve balance.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.thottbot.com/index.cgi?profile=P.Sanghem" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sanghem</a>
<br />
Fires of Heaven</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
